   Super; Microsoft Res; Fundacao Amparo Pesquisa Inovacao Estado Santa
   Catarina; Conselho Nacil Desenvolvimento Cientifico Tecnologico;
   Financiadora Estudos Projetos},
Abstract = {More and more, data extracted from social networks is used to build new
   applications and services, such as traffic monitoring platforms,
   identification of epidemic outbreaks, as well as several other
   applications related to the creation of smart cities, for example.
   However, such services are vulnerable to attacks from bots - automatized
   accounts - seeking to tamper statistics of public perception posting an
