   sensors will play a determining role in Intelligent Transportation
   System (ITS) and Smart City applications. With the evolution of VANET
   services comes the need for solutions to increase the availability of
   content to users. To this end, we propose a Geo-Localized
   Origin-Destination-based Content Replication (GO-DCR) solution that
   relies on vehicles' origin and destination points to decide which of
   them are more appropriate to replicate content inside a region of
   interest. We compare GO-DCR with two existing solutions through
