Abstract = {Vehicle-based sensing is a valuable paradigm to serve third-party
   applications, but understanding the coverage of such networks is not
   trivial. For urban buses, trajectories are spatially predictable, but
   traffic conditions can hinder data timeliness. In this letter, we
